ally come out to a win for everybody this might even solve the nc problem for many of us if for example there were a registry where you could look up any cc by nc work and determine what fee would be asked for licensing to cc by sa or what would be required for incorporation into a larger proprietary work the latter service is provided by magnatune for example but not the former cheers terry terry hancock hancock anansispaceworks com anansi spaceworks http www anansispaceworks com cc community mailing list cc community lists ibiblio org http lists ibiblio org mailman listinfo cc community